WEBVTT

00:01.627 --> 00:03.709
[ CLATTERING 1

00:03.921 --> 00:05.786
[ SHOUTING
IN NATIVE LANGUAGE]

00:09.051 --> 00:11.007
I'M SORRY! SOR--

00:11.220 --> 00:12.881
[ GRUNTING 1

00:21.189 --> 00:26.684
BOTH: THREE-1,000, FOUR-1,000,
FIVE-1,000, SIX-1,000,

00:26.903 --> 00:28.939
SEVEN-1,000, EIGHT-1,000,

00:29.155 --> 00:30.691
NINE-1,000, TEN-1,000.

00:30.907 --> 00:32.898
READY OR NOT,
HERE WE COME!

00:51.802 --> 00:53.178
HYAH!

00:58.684 --> 00:59.844
DYLAN:
SAY YOUR PRAYERS, INDIAN.

01:00.061 --> 01:01.221
[TOY GUN CLICKING]
[ GASPING 1

01:10.613 --> 01:14.197
[ENGINE SHUTS OFF]
NEEL! I GOT HER!

01:23.417 --> 01:25.874
NEEL?

01:36.055 --> 01:39.547
CHARLIE: I LOOKED EVERYWHERE.
I'VE CALLED ALL THE NEIGHBORS.

01:39.767 --> 01:41.974
MR. FIELDING?
PLEASE, SIT DOWN.

01:42.186 --> 01:44.017
YOU NEED TO PUT OUT AN AMBER
ALERT OR SOMETHING, RIGHT?

01:44.230 --> 01:46.221
I MEAN,
ALL WE HAVE Is HIs SHOE.

01:46.440 --> 01:48.180
THAT'S MY SON!

01:49.360 --> 01:51.271
NEEL IS OUR FOSTER SON.

01:51.487 --> 01:52.772
HE'S BEEN WITH US
FIVE MONTHS.

01:52.989 --> 01:54.195
CHARLIE: HE WAS PLAYING
WITH OUR DAUGHTER, ADDYSON,

01:54.407 --> 01:56.398
AND OUR NEIGHBOR'S BOY,
DYLAN,

01:56.617 --> 01:58.448
IN THE EMPTY LOT
AT THE DEAD END.

01:58.661 --> 01:59.741
DO YOU REMEMBER
SEEING OR HEARING

01:59.954 --> 02:01.239
ANYTHING ELSE
IN THE WOODS?

02:01.455 --> 02:04.868
JUST THAT HIS HORSE WAS THERE,
BUT HE WASN'T.

02:07.003 --> 02:08.288
HAS NEEL EVER TRIED
TO RUN AWAY BEFORE?

02:08.504 --> 02:09.619
TRACY: NEVER.

02:09.839 --> 02:12.171
WE WERE TWO WEEKS AWAY
FROM ADOPTING HIM.

02:12.383 --> 02:13.418
FROM WHAT WE'VE HEARD,

02:13.634 --> 02:15.044
NEEL'S BIRTH PARENTS
ARE A REAL MESS.

02:15.261 --> 02:16.671
THEY'RE ADDICTS, I THINK.

02:16.887 --> 02:19.594
NOW, MAYBE THEY FOUND US.
MAYBE THEY TOOK HIM.

02:19.807 --> 02:21.422
I'M GOING TO THE RESERVATION
TO LOOK.

02:21.642 --> 02:23.473
BETTER IF YOU STAY HERE AND
DON'T JUMP TO ANY CONCLUSIONS.

02:23.686 --> 02:25.722
THERE'S NO TIME!
YES, THERE IS.

02:25.938 --> 02:27.894
THIS IS ALL HARD TO BELIEVE,
I KNOW.

02:28.107 --> 02:30.268
WE GET A FEW CASES LIKE THIS
EVERY YEAR.

02:30.484 --> 02:32.566
USUALLY, THE CHILD COMES BACK
IN AN HOUR OR TWO

02:32.778 --> 02:33.893
WITH A LINE OF TROUT,

02:34.113 --> 02:36.104
WONDERING WHY
EVERYBODY'S SO UPSET.

02:36.324 --> 02:38.906
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

02:39.118 --> 02:41.029
VIC: I NEED YOU TO PUT OUT
A STATEWIDE BROADCAST.

02:41.245 --> 02:42.451
MONTANA, TOO.

02:42.663 --> 02:45.700
NEEL CODY, 8.
I JUST TEXTED YOU A PHOTO.

02:45.916 --> 02:48.293
HANG ON.

02:48.502 --> 02:50.288
YEAH, BRANCH.

02:50.504 --> 02:52.711
CHECK THE REGISTERED
SEX OFFENDERS IN THE COUNTY --

02:52.923 --> 02:55.130
AN ALIBI CHECK
ON EVERY ONE OF THEM.

02:55.343 --> 02:56.753
UH-HUH, GOOD.

02:56.969 --> 02:58.209
YOU EVER RUN AWAY
FROM HOME?

02:58.429 --> 03:00.545
YEAH, ONCE,
WHEN I WAs 13.

03:00.765 --> 03:02.551
LOST MY TEMPER.

03:02.767 --> 03:04.473
WALKED OUT OF THE HOUSE
IN THE MIDDLE OF WINTER.

03:04.685 --> 03:06.016
HAVE YOUR SHOES ON?

03:06.228 --> 03:08.640
BOOTS, I THINK.

03:08.856 --> 03:10.062
KID DOESN'T RUN AWAY
WITH JUST ONE SHOE

03:10.274 --> 03:12.481
UNLESS HE WANTS TO RUN
IN CIRCLES.

03:12.693 --> 03:14.308
WHAT ARE
YOU THINKING?

03:14.528 --> 03:16.189
CAN'T DISCOUNT
WHAT MR. FIELDING SAID

03:16.405 --> 03:17.906
ABOUT NEEL'S
BIOLOGICAL PARENTS.

03:18.115 --> 03:21.733
AND HALF OF ALL ABDUCTIONS
ARE FAMILY MEMBERS --

03:21.952 --> 03:23.863
CUSTODY DISPUTES.

03:24.080 --> 03:25.695
WELL, IF YOU'RE GONNA TAKE A KID
IN BROAD DAYLIGHT,

03:25.915 --> 03:27.075
THIS IS AS GOOD A PLACE
AS ANY.

03:27.291 --> 03:31.455
TREES FOR COVER,
A ROAD TO GET AWAY.

03:31.671 --> 03:33.081
NO SCREAMS.

03:33.297 --> 03:35.083
WHAT?

03:35.299 --> 03:37.290
THE DAUGHTER NEVER SAID ANYTHING
ABOUT ANY SCREAMS,

03:37.510 --> 03:40.297
SO NEEL EITHER
DIDN'T SEE HIS ATTACKER

03:40.513 --> 03:44.927
AND THE PERSON
COVERED HIS MOUTH OR...

03:45.142 --> 03:48.009
NEEL SAW A FACE
THAT DIDN'T SCARE HIM.

03:48.229 --> 03:51.517
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK
OR WHAT YOU HOPE?

04:19.343 --> 04:22.130
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

04:25.057 --> 04:28.845
VIC: HI.

04:29.061 --> 04:30.221
WHAT'S THAT,
A DINOSAUR?

04:30.438 --> 04:31.848
IT'S A PARASAUROLOPHUS.

04:32.064 --> 04:33.224
[GUN COCKS]

04:35.568 --> 04:38.150
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

04:38.362 --> 04:41.320
MRS. CODY: FIRST YOU TAKE HIM
AWAY, AND THEN YOU LOSE HIM.

04:41.532 --> 04:42.738
MRS. CODY,
WE DIDN'T LOSE NEEL.

04:42.950 --> 04:44.360
WE'RE JUST
TRYING TO LOCATE HIM.

04:44.577 --> 04:46.067
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY
"TAKE HIM AWAY"?

04:46.287 --> 04:48.118
THEY TOOK OUR SON
RIGHT OUT OF SCHOOL

04:48.330 --> 04:49.615
AND PUT HIM
IN A FOSTER HOME.

04:49.832 --> 04:51.743
DIDN'T EVEN HAVE THE DECENCY
TO TELL US.

04:51.959 --> 04:53.540
"THEY"?
FAMILY SERVICES.

04:53.753 --> 04:56.039
TOLD US IT WAS
FOR NEEL'S OWN GOOD.

04:56.255 --> 04:57.711
THEY SAID
WE WERE ADDICTS.

04:57.923 --> 04:59.788
SAID A NEIGHBOR TALKED ABOUT
ABUSE AND NEGLECT IN OUR HOUSE.

05:00.009 --> 05:02.000
ALL LIES.

05:02.219 --> 05:04.756
DID YOU TRY TO FIGHT IT
IN THE COURT?
[SCOFFS]

05:04.972 --> 05:07.384
A CHEYENNE IN A WHITE COURT.
EVER READ HISTORY?

05:07.600 --> 05:08.760
THAT'S NOT WHAT I MEANT.
| --

05:08.976 --> 05:10.261
EVER TRY TO VISIT NEEL
IN THE FOSTER HOME?

05:10.478 --> 05:13.185
I WALK 3 1/2 MILES
TO MY DAY JOB.

05:13.397 --> 05:15.183
MINIMUM WAGE, PART TIME.

05:15.399 --> 05:17.185
I COME HOME, I SHUT MY EYES
FOR A FEW MINUTES,

05:17.401 --> 05:18.686
THEN I HEAD OUT
TO MY NIGHT JOB.

05:18.903 --> 05:20.393
IN A MONTH,
IF NO ONE GETS SICK,

05:20.613 --> 05:23.070
MAYBE I HAVE THE MONEY TO FINISH
REBUILDING THAT ENGINE.

05:23.282 --> 05:25.819
THEN MAYBE I'LL FIND SOMETHING
FULL TIME WITH BETTER PAY.

05:26.035 --> 05:27.445
AND THEN WE CAN TALK ABOUT
HIRING A LAWYER

05:27.661 --> 05:28.946
TO GET NEEL BACK.

05:31.874 --> 05:33.080
RU BY.

05:33.292 --> 05:35.078
THIS WEEK'S FAN MAIL
AND LOVE LETTERS.

05:35.294 --> 05:37.501
I PUT TOGETHER
AN IMPROMPTU PRESS CONFERENCE

05:37.713 --> 05:39.328
WITH A MOBILE UNIT
FROM CASPER.

05:39.548 --> 05:40.958
THEY'LL SHARE THE VIDEO
WITH THE OTHER NETWORKS.

05:41.175 --> 05:42.585
SHOULD BE ON EVERY TV SET
IN THE STATE

05:42.802 --> 05:44.383
BY END OF DAY.

05:44.595 --> 05:45.630
ALSO DUG UP
THE ARREST RECORDS

05:45.846 --> 05:47.552
FOR NEEL CODY'S
CHEYENNE FAMILY.

05:47.765 --> 05:51.553
VIC: RECKLESS-DRIVING CITATION
FOR HIS MOTHER FROM 10 YEARS AGO

05:51.769 --> 05:53.725
AND A DROPPED
DRUNK-AND-DISORDERLY
FOR THE FATHER.

05:53.938 --> 05:55.053
THAT'S IT?

05:55.272 --> 05:57.684
MY GRANDMA'S GOT
A LONGER RAP SHEET.

05:57.900 --> 05:59.891
LOOKS LIKE THEIR BIGGEST CRIME'S
JUST BEING POOR.

06:00.110 --> 06:01.486
I GOT TO TELL YOU,
IF SOMEONE WALKED

06:01.695 --> 06:03.356
INTO MY KID'S SCHOOL
AND TOOK MY CHILD AWAY,

06:03.572 --> 06:05.563
I'D BE PISSED ENOUGH TO TAKE
MATTERS INTO MY OWN HANDS.

06:05.783 --> 06:07.193
YOU REALLY THINK THE CAR
WAS BROKE DOWN?

06:07.409 --> 06:09.536
IT WAS. I LOOKED.
NO ALTERNATOR.

06:09.745 --> 06:11.326
THAT DOESN'T MEAN
THEY COULDN'T HAVE BORROWED ONE.

06:11.539 --> 06:13.370
WHERE THERE'S A WILL,
THERE'S A WAY.

06:13.582 --> 06:15.834
I'LL GET THE TRIBAL POLICE
TO KEEP AN EYE ON THE FAMILY.

06:16.001 --> 06:17.332
OH, BRANCH...

06:17.545 --> 06:18.751
YOU FOLLOW UP
ON THE SEX OFFENDERS?

06:18.963 --> 06:20.373
YEP. EIGHT REGISTERED
IN THE COUNTY.

06:20.589 --> 06:22.375
EVERY ONE OF THEM
ACCOUNTED FOR.

06:22.591 --> 06:24.877
GOOD. NOW HEAD OVER TO
THE GROUP HOME WHERE
NEEL USED TO LIVE.

06:25.094 --> 06:26.959
SEE IF HE'S HIDING
WITH ANY OF HIS FRIENDS.

06:31.350 --> 06:32.430
...ADULTS.

06:32.643 --> 06:34.224
YOU SAID
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME, DAD?

06:37.648 --> 06:40.481
VIC:
WE NEED A FAVOR.

06:40.693 --> 06:43.025
A CHEYENNE BOY, NEEL CODY,
HAS GONE MISSING.

06:43.237 --> 06:44.443
WE NEED YOUR HELP.

06:44.655 --> 06:47.271
OH,
THAT'S HORRIBLE.

06:47.491 --> 06:49.698
AND INTERESTING,
BECAUSE MY BOSS IS HANDLING

06:49.910 --> 06:51.696
THE NEEL CODY ADOPTION
FOR THE FIELDINGS.

06:51.912 --> 06:54.654
DAD, I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'RE ASKING ME THIS.

06:54.874 --> 06:56.330
HE'S NOT. I AM.

06:57.626 --> 06:59.582
I UNDERSTAND
IT'S ATTORNEY-CLIENT PRIVILEGE,

06:59.795 --> 07:01.080
BUT ALL I WANT IS
A LEGAL WAY

07:01.297 --> 07:03.003
FOR YOU TO GET US ACCESS
TO NEEL'S FILE.

07:03.215 --> 07:06.127
TRANSLATED IN WYOMING --
YOU WANT ME TO BREAK THE LAW.

07:06.343 --> 07:09.130
NO ONE'S BREAKING THE LAW.
BUT, CADY, UH...

07:09.346 --> 07:11.337
YOU KNOW HOW VOLATILE
THESE CUSTODY BATTLES ARE.

07:11.557 --> 07:12.888
WE'RE TRYING
TO FIND THE TRUTH.

07:13.100 --> 07:15.056
THERE HAVE BEEN A LOT
OF ACCUSATIONS ON BOTH SIDES.

07:15.269 --> 07:17.055
WHICH IS WHY THIS IS
BEING HANDLED IN COURT.

07:17.271 --> 07:19.011
GOD, ARE YOU ALWAYS
SUCH A GOODY-GOODY?

07:19.231 --> 07:21.938
NO. AND THERE'S A DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN BEING A GOODY-GOODY

07:22.151 --> 07:23.812
AND NOT WANTING
TO GET DISBARRED.

07:24.028 --> 07:25.814
VIC, NOW, CADY'S RIGHT.

07:26.030 --> 07:27.816
SHE CAN'T HELP US FIND
THIS POOR MISSING BOY,

07:28.032 --> 07:29.317
EVEN IF SHE WANTS TO.

07:31.160 --> 07:33.196
THANKS FOR COMING BY,
PUNK.

07:35.205 --> 07:38.743
OKAY, LOOK...

07:38.959 --> 07:40.699
I CAN'T TELL YOU ANYTHING
ABOUT THE FIELDING ADOPTION.

07:40.920 --> 07:42.160
THAT'S PRIVATE.

07:42.379 --> 07:43.664
BUT I MIGHT HAVE
SOME INSIGHT

07:43.881 --> 07:45.746
INTO THE BYZANTINE BUREAUCRACY
OF THE STATE.

07:45.966 --> 07:48.799
I'M SORRY. CAN YOU TRANSLATE
THAT INTO PHILADELPHIAN FOR ME?

07:49.011 --> 07:51.297
I MIGHT BE ABLE TO POINT YOU
IN THE DIRECTION

07:51.513 --> 07:52.923
OF SOME PUBLIC RECORDS

07:53.140 --> 07:54.755
THAT ARE NOT COVERED
BY ATTORNEY-CLIENT PRIVILEGE.

07:56.852 --> 07:59.514
RYAN: IT ISN'T LIKE NEEL
TO RUN AWAY.

07:59.730 --> 08:02.346
[SIGHS]

08:02.566 --> 08:04.522
I'M JUST WORRIED SICK.

08:04.735 --> 08:06.350
YOU HAVE ANY OPINION
ON THE FIELDINGS?

08:06.570 --> 08:08.652
I TRY TO BE IMPARTIAL,
BUT I MUST SAY,

08:08.864 --> 08:11.105
I WISH MORE FOSTER PARENTS
WERE LIKE THEM.

08:11.325 --> 08:13.862
WHAT ABOUT
NEEL'S BIOLOGICAL PARENTS?

08:14.078 --> 08:16.239
YOU HEAR ANY STORIES ABOUT THEM?
THEY EVER COME AROUND?

08:16.455 --> 08:20.448
NO. I MEAN, THIS KIDS
ARE THROWAWAY KIDS.

08:20.668 --> 08:23.705
I MEAN, ONCE THEY LEAVE THE RES,
THEY'RE KIND OF FORGOTTEN.

08:23.921 --> 08:25.161
I MEAN, I DON'T MEAN
TO SOUND RACIST.

08:25.381 --> 08:26.791
IT'S JUST THE WAY IT IS.
OKAY.

08:27.007 --> 08:29.999
YOU WOULDN'T HAPPEN TO HAVE
NEEL'S PAPERWORK, WOULD YOU?

08:30.219 --> 08:32.835
CHAOS IS SORT OF OUR ORGANIZING
PRINCIPLE AROUND HERE.

08:33.055 --> 08:35.797
NEEL'S PAPERS ARE PROBABLY
DOWN WITH COUNTY ALREADY.

08:36.016 --> 08:38.632
WELL,
IF YOU HEAR ANYTHING...

08:38.852 --> 08:40.467
GIVE A CALL.

08:40.688 --> 08:41.973
SMALLEST THING MAY HELP.

08:43.857 --> 08:46.564
[SIGHS] I HEARD YOU
THE FIRST TIME, MATHIAS.

08:46.777 --> 08:49.735
ALL I'M ASKING IS YOU KEEP
AN EYE ON THE CODY HOUSE.

08:53.492 --> 08:55.198
YEAH.

08:55.411 --> 08:56.821
ALWAYS A PLEASURE.

08:58.539 --> 09:00.575
[ RAIN FALLING ]

09:08.882 --> 09:11.840
[ KNOCK ON DOOR]
RUBY: SHERIFF?

09:13.262 --> 09:15.173
WE GOT A CRYING WOMAN
IN OUR LOBBY.

09:17.766 --> 09:21.008
MY SON IS MISSING.

09:21.228 --> 09:22.434
HOW OLD IS HE?

09:22.646 --> 09:24.227
35.

09:24.440 --> 09:26.431
YOUR 35-YEAR-OLD SON
IS MISSING?

09:26.650 --> 09:29.437
[VOICE BREAKING ] AND THEN
I SAW THAT TELEVISION REPORT,

09:29.653 --> 09:31.268
AND I KNEW
I HAD TO COME IN,

09:31.488 --> 09:34.696
BUT I...JUST COULDN'T MAKE
MYSELF COME THROUGH THE DOOR.

09:34.908 --> 09:37.285
SLOW DOWN, MA'AM. NOW...
NOW, WHAT'S YOUR SON'S NAME?

09:37.494 --> 09:41.203
JEREMY --
JEREMY THOMPSON.

09:41.415 --> 09:43.747
HE HASN'T RETURNED
ANY OF MY CALLS.

09:43.959 --> 09:47.451
I'M AFRAID FOR HIM, SHERIFF,
FOR WHAT HE MIGHT HAVE DONE.

09:47.671 --> 09:50.333
WHY ARE YOU WORRIED
ABOUT JEREMY?

09:50.549 --> 09:55.964
HE WAS A [SNIFFLES]
TEACHER'S AIDE IN TULSA.

09:56.180 --> 09:59.388
THEY SAID HE...

09:59.600 --> 10:03.513
TOUCHED ONE OR TWO
OF THE BOYS.

10:03.729 --> 10:05.640
HE ADMITTED TO HIS SIN.

10:05.856 --> 10:07.642
HE DID HIS TIME,

10:07.858 --> 10:11.066
AND THEN HE MOVED BACK
TO LIVE WITH ME ABOUT A YEAR AGO

10:11.278 --> 10:12.893
SO THAT
I COULD HELP HIM.

10:13.113 --> 10:14.569
YOUR SON
IS A SEX OFFENDER?

10:15.991 --> 10:18.858
HE NEVER REGISTERED.
[SOBS]

10:19.078 --> 10:22.866
I DIDN'T WANT HIM PERSECUTED.
HE PROMISED ME.

10:23.082 --> 10:26.370
I WANTED HIM TO HAVE
A FRESH START, BUT --

10:26.585 --> 10:32.330
BUT NOW I FEAR EVIL
HAS GOT HOLD OF HIM AGAIN.

10:32.549 --> 10:35.757
RUBY, PUT OUT AN AMBER ALERT
FOR NEEL CODY NOW.

10:35.969 --> 10:38.051
WE GOT TO FIND THIS BOY,
AND SOON.

10:38.263 --> 10:40.595
[ STATIC ]

10:40.808 --> 10:44.016
RUBY: THE SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT
OF ABSAROKA COUNTY, WYOMING,

10:44.228 --> 10:48.847
IS ISSUING AN AMBER ALERT
FOR A MISSING 8-YEAR-OLD BOY --

10:49.066 --> 10:50.681
NEEL CODY.

10:50.901 --> 10:52.311
IN CONNECTION
WITH THIS ABDUCTION,

10:52.528 --> 10:55.315
WE ARE SEEKING A MAN NAMED
JEREMY THOMPSON,

10:55.531 --> 11:01.492
DRIVING A SILVER-AND-WHITE
1995 FORD F-350 PICKUP

11:01.703 --> 11:03.489
WITH WYOMING LICENSE...

11:03.705 --> 11:04.911
LIGHTS OUT, GUYS.

11:05.124 --> 11:10.209
..."24-30-C-6-H ."

11:12.131 --> 11:13.837
WE HAVE REASON TO BELIEVE

11:14.049 --> 11:16.540
THE CHILD IS
IN IMMINENT DANGER.

11:26.353 --> 11:29.516
[ SCUFFLING ]

11:44.454 --> 11:46.069
YOU SAID THERE WERE
TWO MISSING CHEYENNE BOYS.

11:46.290 --> 11:47.996
I PULLED IN AT 6:00 A.M.,
AND MY SUPERVISOR'S
NOT EVEN HERE.

11:48.208 --> 11:51.200
NO NOTE, NO NOTHING.
YOUR SUPERVISOR --
IS THAT RYAN SHANK?

11:51.420 --> 11:53.251
YEAH. I'VE TRIED CALLING.
NO ANSWER.

11:53.463 --> 11:55.954
NEEL CODY, ANOTHER
CHEYENNE FOSTER CHILD,

11:56.175 --> 11:57.460
WAS ABDUCTED YESTERDAY.

11:57.676 --> 11:59.212
NOW TWO MORE
ARE MISSING.

11:59.428 --> 12:01.043
THAT'S 3
IN LESS THAN 24 HOURS.

12:01.263 --> 12:03.845
OH, GOD.
YOU THINK THEY WERE TAKEN?

12:04.057 --> 12:05.672
IT'S STARTING
TO LOOK THAT WAY.

12:07.686 --> 12:10.928
DID ANY OF YOU SEE
THIS MAN LAST NIGHT?

12:13.734 --> 12:15.816
NO. WE WERE SLEEPING.

12:24.494 --> 12:27.361
WHAT KIND OF CAR
DOES RYAN SHANK DRIVE?

12:27.581 --> 12:29.822
UH, A FORD EXPLORER,
GRAY.

12:30.042 --> 12:32.408
I'LL MAKE SURE
RUBY UPDATES THE AMBER ALERT.

12:32.628 --> 12:35.916
COULD YOU SHOW US
SHANK'S OFFICE?

12:36.131 --> 12:38.122
THESE THE BOYS
THAT WERE TAKEN?

12:38.342 --> 12:40.003
YEAH,
CIERRE AND MICHAEL.

12:40.219 --> 12:41.800
AND RYAN --

12:42.012 --> 12:43.468
HE WOULD DO ANYTHING
TO PROTECT THEM.

12:45.015 --> 12:47.597
ARE THE BOYS' CASE FILES
IN HERE?
THEY SHOULD BE.

12:50.270 --> 12:53.307
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME.

12:57.236 --> 12:59.727
DIDN'T BRANCH SAY
THAT RYAN SHANK SAID

12:59.947 --> 13:01.107
HE WAS GONNA SEND OVER
NEEL CODY'S FILE

13:01.323 --> 13:02.608
AS SOON AS HE GOT IT BACK
FROM THE COUNTY?

13:02.824 --> 13:03.813
THAT'S RIGHT.

13:04.034 --> 13:06.650
IT WAS RIGHT HERE.

13:06.870 --> 13:09.577
RIGHT WITH THE OTHERS.

13:11.458 --> 13:14.700
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

13:14.920 --> 13:16.706
SOMETIMES YOU CAN LEARN
A LOT ABOUT A PERSON

13:16.922 --> 13:18.287
BY LOOKING
AT THEIR BOOKSHELVES.

13:18.507 --> 13:21.590
RIGHT.
AND WHAT HAVE YOU LEARNED?

13:21.802 --> 13:23.963
A LOT OF SCIENCE FICTION --
ASIMOV.

13:25.806 --> 13:27.012
HIGH-SCHOOL YEARBOOKS,

13:27.224 --> 13:29.135
WHICH IS ODD
FOR A MAN SHANK'S AGE.

13:29.351 --> 13:31.637
HE'S EITHER SENTIMENTAL
OR LIVING IN THE PAST.

13:35.732 --> 13:38.064
FOR YEARS,
THE COUNTY HAS BEEN TAKING

13:38.277 --> 13:40.563
CHEYENNE CHILDREN
OFF THE RESERVATION

13:40.779 --> 13:42.394
AND PLACING THEM IN HOMES

13:42.614 --> 13:44.991
RUN BY WHITE MEN
AND WHITE WOMEN.

13:45.200 --> 13:46.940
BUT WE EXPECT THAT, DON'T WE?

13:47.160 --> 13:48.775
WHAT WE DON'T EXPECT IS

13:48.996 --> 13:51.988
FOR THE COUNTY TO MISPLACE
ONE OF THESE CHILDREN.

13:53.125 --> 13:56.413
AND WE DON'T EXPECT
SHERIFF WALT LONGMIRE

13:56.628 --> 14:00.246
TO ALLOW A PEDOPHILE
TO ROAM OUR STREETS AT WILL.

14:00.465 --> 14:02.456
DO YOU THINK THE SHERIFF
WOULD BE DOING SO LITTLE

14:02.676 --> 14:05.383
IF THE PEDOPHILE
WAS A CHEYENNE OR LAKOTA?

14:07.472 --> 14:09.724
YOU BET, HE WOULD NOT.
STILL THINK
YOU WANT MY JOB, BRANCH?

14:09.933 --> 14:12.140
GUY REALLY DOESN'T SEEM
TO LIKE YOU, SHERIFF.

14:12.352 --> 14:13.762
YOU'RE NOT FACEBOOK FRIENDS,
I TAKE IT.

14:13.979 --> 14:15.765
I DON'T EXPECT
EVERYONE TO LIKE ME.

14:15.981 --> 14:17.391
I EXPECT THEM
TO LEAVE POLITICS OUT OF IT

14:17.607 --> 14:19.313
WHEN WE'RE DEALING
WITH MISSING KIDS.

14:19.526 --> 14:22.359
KIDS? PLURAL?

14:22.571 --> 14:25.153
DID RYAN SHANK EVER CALL YOU
ABOUT NEEL'S FILE?

14:25.365 --> 14:28.027
NOT YET. IT SOUNDED
LIKE THERE WAS A LOT
OF RED TAPE INVOLVED.

14:28.243 --> 14:30.325
HE LIED. THE FILE WAS
IN HIS OFFICE THE ENTIRE TIME.

14:30.537 --> 14:32.323
WAS SHANK
UP TO SOMETHING?

14:32.539 --> 14:34.905
HE'S MISSING, ALONG WITH
TWO BOYS FROM THE GROUP HOME.

14:35.125 --> 14:38.083
YOU THINK HE TOOK THEM?
YOU TALKED TO HIM.

14:38.295 --> 14:40.502
YOU GET ANY KIND OF A HIT
OFF HIM?

14:40.714 --> 14:41.999
HE WAS UPSET.

14:42.215 --> 14:44.501
BUT UNDER THE CIRCUMSTANCES,
THAT SEEMED NORMAL.

14:45.802 --> 14:48.088
DIG DEEPER.
VIC, GIVE HIM A HAND.

14:48.305 --> 14:50.091
CONTACT THE MISSING BOYS'
BIOLOGICAL PARENTS,

14:50.307 --> 14:51.592
SEE WHERE THEY WERE
LAST NIGHT.

14:51.808 --> 14:53.548
I'M GONNA GO DEAL
WITH THE BUREAUCRACY.

14:53.769 --> 14:55.680
SEEMS BOTH KIDS
HAD THE SAME SOCIAL WORKER.

14:55.896 --> 14:57.978
MAYBE SHE KNOWS
SOMETHING WORTH KNOWING.

14:59.399 --> 15:01.685
ACCORDING
TO MR. SHANK'S FILES,

15:01.902 --> 15:03.688
YOU HANDLED
ALL THREE BOYS' CASES.

15:03.904 --> 15:05.895
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE
THAT LINKS THEM?

15:06.114 --> 15:09.322
ABUSE, NEGLECT,
MALNOURISHMENT.

15:09.534 --> 15:11.570
THAT'S WHAT LINKS THEM.

15:11.787 --> 15:14.403
UNFORTUNATELY, IT'S ALSO
WHAT MAKES THEM TYPICAL.

15:14.623 --> 15:17.035
THERE ARE SO MANY
NATIVE CHILDREN TO HELP,

15:17.250 --> 15:18.990
BUT WITH
OUR LIMITED RESOURCES,

15:19.211 --> 15:21.327
THERE'S ONLY SO MUCH
WE CAN DO.

15:21.546 --> 15:23.502
DO YOU HAVE MUCH CONTACT
WITH RYAN SHANK,

15:23.715 --> 15:24.875
THE GROUP-HOME SUPERVISOR?

15:25.092 --> 15:26.377
I DO. WHY?

15:26.593 --> 15:28.925
YOU THINK SHANK MIGHT HAVE
ACTED INAPPROPRIATELY

15:29.137 --> 15:30.252
WITH THESE KIDS?

15:31.640 --> 15:33.926
OH, WOW. I, UM...

15:34.142 --> 15:35.678
[SIGHS]

15:35.894 --> 15:39.682
LOOK, YOU HAVE TO BE
VERY CAREFUL

15:39.898 --> 15:41.763
WITH THOSE KINDS
OF ACCUSATIONS AND RUMORS

15:41.983 --> 15:43.359
WHEN YOU'RE WORKING
WITH KIDS.

15:43.568 --> 15:45.149
RIGHT NOW, WE'RE JUST
TRYING TO FIND HIM.

15:45.362 --> 15:46.943
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU SPOKE WITH HIM?

15:47.155 --> 15:48.361
LAST NIGHT.

15:48.573 --> 15:50.564
IT WAS A PRETTY MUNDANE
CONVERSATION,

15:50.784 --> 15:53.196
BUT IT WAS...WEIRD
THAT HE CALLED SO LATE.

15:53.412 --> 15:54.822
LITTLE AFTER 1 0:30.

15:55.038 --> 15:58.371
YOU DEALT WITH
ANY EMOTIONAL PARENTS LATELY?

15:58.583 --> 16:01.325
NO, BUT, UH...

16:01.545 --> 16:06.164
I DID HAVE A CHEYENNE GENTLEMAN
VISIT ME RECENTLY,

16:06.383 --> 16:08.544
UM, ABOUT
A FRIEND'S SITUATION.

16:08.760 --> 16:10.341
I TRIED TO EXPLAIN TO HIM

16:10.554 --> 16:12.169
THE PROPER GUIDELINES
FOR APPEAL,

16:12.389 --> 16:14.880
BUT HE WAS NOT INTERESTED
IN HAVING THAT CONVERSATION.

16:15.100 --> 16:17.307
HE BECAME ENRAGED.

16:17.519 --> 16:20.602
THE CHILD THAT MAN CAME
TO DISCUSS, CIERRE --

16:20.814 --> 16:23.851
HE WAS ONE OF THE BOYS TAKEN
FROM THE GROUP HOME LAST NIGHT.

16:24.067 --> 16:27.400
HENRY:
I WAS NOT ENRAGED.

16:27.612 --> 16:29.603
I WAS INSISTENT.

16:29.823 --> 16:32.405
SHE SAID YOU WERE POUNDING
ON HER DESK.

16:32.617 --> 16:33.777
A RHETORICAL FLOURISH.

16:33.994 --> 16:36.110
HENRY,
WHY WERE YOU EVEN THERE?

16:36.329 --> 16:38.160
THEY TOOK
CISSY PONSON'S SON.

16:38.373 --> 16:40.864
THEY CLAIM SHE WAS
A FALLING-DOWN DRUNK,

16:41.042 --> 16:43.374
THAT HER CAR WAS
HERE AT THE RED PONY
MORNING, NOON, AND NIGHT.

16:43.587 --> 16:45.168
WAS THAT THE CASE?

16:45.380 --> 16:49.373
CISSY PONSON
IS MY EMPLOYEE.

16:49.593 --> 16:52.050
A SINGLE MOTHER.
SHE DOES NOT DRINK.

16:52.262 --> 16:55.629
WHAT DID THE SOCIAL WORKER SAY
WHEN YOU TOLD HER THIS?

16:55.849 --> 16:57.714
SHE SAID THERE WAS NOTHING
SHE COULD DO.

16:57.934 --> 17:00.141
WOW.

17:00.353 --> 17:02.969
I ASSUME YOU KNOW THAT
CISSY'S SON HAS GONE MISSING.

17:03.190 --> 17:04.851
JACOB NIGHTHORSE TOLD ME.

17:05.066 --> 17:07.478
[CHUCKLES]
HE SEEMS TO BE TAKING

17:07.694 --> 17:09.901
A PARTICULAR INTEREST
IN THIS MATTER.

17:10.113 --> 17:11.228
GOOD.
EVERYONE SHOULD.

17:11.448 --> 17:13.188
A PEDOPHILE
IS ON THE LOOSE.

17:13.408 --> 17:16.241
I WANT TO FIND THESE BOYS
AS MUCH AS HE DOES.

17:16.453 --> 17:18.944
THE MORE NIGHTHORSE MAKES THIS
A POLITICAL ISSUE,

17:19.164 --> 17:21.155
THE HARDER IT IS
FOR US TO DO OUR JOB.

17:21.374 --> 17:23.751
OR MAYBE HE IS MAKING SURE
YOU ALL DO YOUR JOB.

17:23.960 --> 17:26.747
[SIGHS]

17:26.963 --> 17:29.705
I APOLOGIZE.

17:31.426 --> 17:32.962
BUT, WALT,
YOU HAVE TO UNDERSTAND

17:33.178 --> 17:35.043
HOW UPSETTING
THIS SITUATION IS ON THE RES.

17:35.263 --> 17:37.049
THERE USED TO BE A SAYING

17:37.265 --> 17:40.007
AMONG THE WHITE PEOPLE
WHO SETTLED THE WEST --

17:40.227 --> 17:43.845
"KILL THE INDIAN,
SAVE THE MAN."

17:44.064 --> 17:47.147
SOMETIMES IT SEEMS LIKE
NOTHING HAS CHANGED.

17:53.156 --> 17:56.114
[SIGHS]

18:02.123 --> 18:04.614
NO CREAM...

18:04.834 --> 18:06.165
TWO SUGARS.

18:07.921 --> 18:09.752
THANKS.

18:09.965 --> 18:12.923
GOT TO SAY, I'M SURPRISED TO SEE
YOU COMPROMISING YOUR ETHICS.

18:13.134 --> 18:16.342
THERE'S NO COMPROMISE.
THESE ARE ALL PUBLIC RECORDS.

18:16.555 --> 18:18.671
THERE'S NOTHING UNETHICAL
ABOUT HELPING ALL OF YOU

18:18.890 --> 18:21.927
NAVIGATE
THE STATE BUREAUCRACY.

18:22.143 --> 18:24.304
BESIDES, EVEN THOUGH
NEEL'S A CLIENT, THE
OTHER TWO BOYS AREN'T.

18:27.440 --> 18:29.726
SHIT. HEY, WALT!

18:29.943 --> 18:31.683
WALT!

18:33.572 --> 18:34.652
SHANK AND JEREMY THOMPSON

18:34.864 --> 18:36.070
WRESTLED TOGETHER
IN HIGH SCHOOL.

18:36.283 --> 18:37.489
THEY KNOW EACH OTHER.

18:37.701 --> 18:39.111
CADY:
OKAY, THAT IS CREEPY.

18:39.327 --> 18:40.942
YOU THINK THEY HAD
AN ARRANGEMENT OR SOMETHING?

18:41.162 --> 18:42.663
LIKE A CHILD-SEX RING?

18:42.872 --> 18:44.487
WHY WOULD RYAN SHANK
ABDUCT THESE BOYS

18:44.708 --> 18:46.494
WHEN HE COULD JUST WALK
RIGHT DOWN THE HALL?

18:46.710 --> 18:49.577
FOR MONEY?
RUBY:
THE AMBER ALERT WORKED!

18:49.796 --> 18:50.706
THEY GOT HIM.

18:50.922 --> 18:54.289
WHICH "HIM"?

19:05.061 --> 19:07.017
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

19:07.230 --> 19:08.094
[ GRUNTING ]

19:08.315 --> 19:10.647
HEY, GUYS, KNOCK IT OFF!

19:10.859 --> 19:12.975
MAN: WE GOT HIM!
WE GOT HIM!
HEY, COME ON!

19:14.195 --> 19:16.447
THE KIDS ARE IN THERE!

19:18.617 --> 19:19.948
[GUNSHOT]

19:22.912 --> 19:27.030
JEREMY...
MIND IF WE TALK?

19:27.250 --> 19:28.239
[VIC GRUNTS]

19:28.460 --> 19:30.826
YOU CAN'T DO THAT.
I GOT RIGHTS.

19:31.046 --> 19:32.252
SO DO WE.

19:36.092 --> 19:37.957
WHAT ARE THESE?

19:38.178 --> 19:40.169
JEREMY: THEY'RE VATS
FOR HEATING CANDLE WAX.

19:40.388 --> 19:42.595
MY BOSS HAD ME DRIVE OVER
TO SALT LAKE TO PICK THEM UP,

19:42.807 --> 19:44.798
AND NOW I'M GONNA BE LATE
FOR MY DELIVERY.

19:45.018 --> 19:46.804
THEN WHY DIDN'T YOU
JUST UNLOCK THE DAMN DOOR?

19:47.020 --> 19:49.227
'CAUSE THESE JERKS AREN'T COPS,
AND YOU NEED A WARRANT.

19:49.439 --> 19:51.521
THAT'S THE LAW.

19:53.568 --> 19:56.435
SO IS REGISTERING
AS A SEX OFFENDER.

20:00.075 --> 20:02.316
DON'T MOVE.

20:02.535 --> 20:05.026
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

20:06.956 --> 20:08.287
[ DOOR OPENS ]

20:08.500 --> 20:10.661
WELL, LOOKY HERE.
IS THIS THE PERVERT?

20:10.877 --> 20:13.289
JACOB,
HOW CAN I HELP YOU?

20:13.505 --> 20:15.712
HAS HE TOLD YOU
WHERE THE KIDS ARE?

20:15.924 --> 20:18.540
HE'S NOT TALKING.
THAT'S HIS RIGHT, SO...

20:18.760 --> 20:20.751
OH, YEAH?
WELL, THAT'S GOOD TO KNOW.

20:20.970 --> 20:22.710
WHAT ABOUT THE RIGHTS
OF THE CHILDREN?

20:22.931 --> 20:25.047
WHAT'S YOUR ANGLE HERE?

20:25.266 --> 20:26.392
WHAT?

20:26.601 --> 20:28.102
I DON'T THINK
YOU'D TAKE A GLASS OF WATER

20:28.311 --> 20:30.017
IF THERE WEREN'T SOME KIND
OF PROFIT INVOLVED.

20:30.230 --> 20:32.642
THERE IS AN ANGLE HERE, SHERIFF,
BUT IT'S NOT MINE.

20:32.857 --> 20:36.349
A WHOLE LOT OF MONEY IS BEING
MADE OFF OF OUR CHILDREN.

20:36.569 --> 20:39.026
EACH OF THESE FOSTER HOMES
RECEIVES FEDERAL MONEY

20:39.239 --> 20:40.775
FOR THE CHILDREN
IN ITS CARE,

20:40.990 --> 20:43.197
BUT THEY GET DOUBLE
FOR INDIAN KIDS.

20:43.410 --> 20:44.820
DOUBLE.

20:45.036 --> 20:47.618
YOU KNOW, TO MOTIVATE
FOSTER FAMILIES TO TAKE THEM IN.

20:47.831 --> 20:49.446
THAT'S A GOOD THING.

20:49.666 --> 20:53.079
NOT WHEN THEY'VE BEEN KIDNAPPED
FROM GOOD CHEYENNE FAMILIES.

20:53.294 --> 20:54.500
ARE YOU SAYING

20:54.713 --> 20:56.578
PEOPLE ARE KIDNAPPING
THESE CHILDREN FOR PROFIT?

20:56.798 --> 20:58.959
NOT PEOPLE.
YOUR GOVERNMENT.

21:02.053 --> 21:03.918
BRANCH, COME IN HERE.

21:04.139 --> 21:05.345
NIGHTHORSE
WANTS TO TALK POLITICS.

21:05.557 --> 21:06.967
I GOT WORK TO DO.
LET'S GO.

21:07.183 --> 21:09.174
RUBY, TELL HENRY
WE'RE ON OUR WAY.

21:09.394 --> 21:10.930
WHERE ARE WE GOING?

21:11.146 --> 21:15.936
LUKE, YOU DIDN'T SPEAK UP
WHEN I WAS HERE BEFORE, BUT...

21:16.151 --> 21:19.814
I REALLY NEED TO KNOW...

21:20.029 --> 21:21.644
HAVE YOU SEEN THIS MAN?

21:21.865 --> 21:25.198
I DON'T WANT TO MAKE
ANY MORE TROUBLE.

21:40.216 --> 21:42.298
THESE ARE GOOD PEOPLE,
LUKE.

21:42.510 --> 21:44.717
THEY'RE MY FRIENDS.

21:44.929 --> 21:48.763
YOU'RE NOT IN TROUBLE.
ALL WE WANT TO DO IS HELP.

21:50.226 --> 21:52.182
DID YOU SEE THIS MAN?

21:58.860 --> 22:01.021
I SAW HOTAMETANEO'O.

22:02.655 --> 22:04.782
GRANDMA ALWAYS TOLD ME
THAT IF I DIDN'T BEHAVE,

22:04.991 --> 22:08.028
THEN HOTAMETANEO'O WOULD
COME THROUGH THE WINDOW
AND TAKE ME AWAY.

22:08.244 --> 22:12.032
VIC: I'M -- I'M -- I'M SORRY.
HOTA-- HOTAMETA--

22:12.248 --> 22:14.830
H-HELP ME.

22:15.043 --> 22:16.829
THERE WAS A BAND
OF CHEYENNE WARRIORS
IN THE 19TH CENTURY.

22:17.045 --> 22:20.162
THEY WERE CALLED HOTAMETANEO'O,
OR DOG SOLDIERS.

22:20.381 --> 22:22.542
IT WAS BELIEVED
THEY COULD CHANGE SHAPE

22:22.759 --> 22:24.795
FROM MAN TO DOG...

22:25.887 --> 22:29.129
...AND BACK AGAIN.

22:29.349 --> 22:31.089
I BROKE MR. SHANK'S RADIO
THIS WEEK.

22:31.309 --> 22:33.300
THAT'S WHY
HOTAMETANEO'O CAME.

22:33.520 --> 22:35.932
WHEN DID
THE DOG SOLDIER APPEAR?

22:36.147 --> 22:38.229
RIGHT AT MIDNIGHT,
AS GRANDMA ALWAYS SAID.

22:38.441 --> 22:40.978
HOW DID YOU KNOW
IT WAS HIM?

22:41.194 --> 22:42.809
I SAW HIS FACE.

22:43.029 --> 22:44.018
AND WHAT
DID HE LOOK LIKE?

22:44.239 --> 22:46.400
HE LOOKS LIKE A SOLDIER.

22:46.616 --> 22:48.607
HE HAD A SCAR
RIGHT THROUGH HERE.

22:49.953 --> 22:53.366
HENRY: EACH DOG SOLDIER
WORE A LEATHER STRAP.

22:53.581 --> 22:54.991
THEY WOULD STAKE THAT STRAP
TO THE GROUND

22:55.208 --> 22:56.448
AND FIGHT TO THE DEATH.

22:56.668 --> 22:59.455
THESE MEN WERE FIGURES
OF DEFIANCE, FIGURES OF HOPE.

22:59.671 --> 23:02.879
THE U.S. ARMY
HUNTED THEM DOWN ONE BY ONE,

23:03.091 --> 23:05.082
BUT THERE WERE RUMORS
OF ONE REMAINING SURVIVOR.

23:05.301 --> 23:06.916
AND THIS IS WHO LUKE SAW
LAST NIGHT?

23:07.136 --> 23:08.125
YES.
NO.

23:08.346 --> 23:10.007
WELL, WHICH IS IT?

23:10.223 --> 23:11.429
IT WAS NO SPIRIT.

23:11.641 --> 23:13.632
THAT KID SAW HECTOR.
YOU DO NOT KNOW THAT.

23:13.852 --> 23:16.138
HENRY,
LUKE DESCRIBED THE SCAR.

23:16.354 --> 23:18.515
BUT KIDNAPPING HAS NEVER BEEN
A PART OF HECTOR'S REPERTOIRE.

23:18.731 --> 23:20.722
OKAY, I'M SORRY.
WHO IS HECTOR?

23:20.942 --> 23:23.183
HECTOR IS A FORMER BOXER
WHO LIVES ON THE RESERVATION.

23:23.403 --> 23:25.234
SINCE MOST CHEYENNE
DO NOT TRUST THE COURTS,

23:25.446 --> 23:27.232
THEY OFTEN HIRE HECTOR
TO RIGHT THEIR WRONGS.

23:27.448 --> 23:28.858
WHICH MEANS HE MAKES HIS LIVING
KNOCKING OUT THE TEETH

23:29.075 --> 23:31.031
OF THIEVES, RAPISTS, THUGS,
AND WIFE-BEATERS.

23:31.244 --> 23:33.906
HECTOR IS AN UNFORTUNATE
NECESSITY OF RESERVATION LIFE,

23:34.122 --> 23:35.578
BUT A NECESSITY
NEVERTHELESS.

23:35.790 --> 23:37.200
SO, WE SHOW THE KID A PICTURE
OF HECTOR AND JUST --

23:37.417 --> 23:38.748
WE'RE DONE WITH IT.

23:38.960 --> 23:40.416
I WOULD
IF ONE WERE KNOWN TO EXIST.

23:40.628 --> 23:44.041
RUBY: WALT! WALT!

23:44.257 --> 23:45.667
WHAT IS IT?

23:45.884 --> 23:47.670
HIGHWAY PATROL
FOUND RYAN SHANK'S CAR.

23:47.886 --> 23:50.593
IT'S NEAR SPOTTED HORSE
IN CAMPBELL COUNTY.

23:50.805 --> 23:54.047
WHAT'S IT DOING
WAY OUT THERE?

23:54.267 --> 23:56.349
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

23:58.438 --> 24:01.726
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER]

24:03.860 --> 24:06.146
FOUND IT RIGHT HERE.

24:06.362 --> 24:07.977
KEYS ARE
IN THE IGNITION.

24:12.118 --> 24:13.654
VIC: HERE, BOY.

24:13.870 --> 24:16.327
[ SMOOCHING ]

24:16.539 --> 24:18.075
AWW. COME HERE.

24:25.048 --> 24:27.505
THAT BETTER NOT BE
A CHILD'S EAR.

24:43.942 --> 24:45.853
IT'S NOT A KID.

24:47.862 --> 24:49.648
VIC: IT'S A SHANK.

24:49.864 --> 24:52.606
WHAT DO YOU THINK,
HENRY?

24:52.825 --> 24:55.237
HAS THE DOG SOLDIER
STRUCK AGAIN?

25:04.003 --> 25:06.289
WHERE'S JEREMY THOMPSON?

25:06.506 --> 25:09.498
HIS ALIBI CHECKED OUT.
HAD TO RELEASE HIM.

25:11.970 --> 25:14.177
IT'S RYAN SHAN K.

25:15.682 --> 25:17.547
THIS IS DEPUTY CONNALLY.

25:17.767 --> 25:19.177
WALT: SHANK'S DEAD.

25:20.478 --> 25:22.218
WHAT HAPPENED?

25:22.438 --> 25:26.977
MURDERED. HAD HIS CELLPHONE
ON HIM AND THIS.

25:27.193 --> 25:29.434
I GAVE HIM THAT
YESTERDAY.

25:29.654 --> 25:31.190
I TOLD HIM TO CALL
IF ANYTHING HAPPENED.
WE GOT A SUSPECT?

25:31.406 --> 25:34.364
WE DO. I'M SENDING YOU TO
THE RESERVATION TO LOOK FOR HIM.

25:34.575 --> 25:37.157
PEOPLE ARE DYING.
WE NEED TO FIND THESE KIDS.

25:37.370 --> 25:39.611
WHO AM I LOOKING FOR?
HECTOR.

25:39.831 --> 25:41.367
THE HECTOR?

25:41.582 --> 25:43.538
TAKE VIC. SHE'LL FILL YOU IN
ON THE WAY.

25:44.794 --> 25:49.083
CADY:
DAD, WHO'S H ECTOR?

25:49.298 --> 25:51.914
UH, I THINK
HE'S THE KIDNAPPER...

25:52.135 --> 25:53.750
AND POSSIBLY NOW
A MURDERER.

25:53.970 --> 25:56.507
DO YOU THINK SHANK WAS KILLED
TRYING TO PROTECT THE BOYS?

25:56.723 --> 25:58.133
I DON'T KNOW.

25:58.349 --> 25:59.759
BECAUSE I MIGHT HAVE FOUND
ANOTHER REASON

25:59.976 --> 26:01.716
WHY SHANK WAS TARGETED.

26:01.936 --> 26:03.551
JACOB NIGHTHORSE
WAS RIGHT.

26:03.771 --> 26:05.181
FOR EVERY
NATIVE AMERICAN KID,

26:05.398 --> 26:07.605
THE FOSTER HOMES GET
NEARLY TWICE AS MUCH MONEY.

26:07.817 --> 26:11.230
AND SHANK'S FACILITY HAS
13 CHEYENNE CHILDREN RIGHT NOW.

26:11.446 --> 26:14.734
IT GETS $700 EXTRA A MONTH
FOR EACH OF THOSE KIDS.

26:14.949 --> 26:17.031
AND WHAT'S ODD IS

26:17.243 --> 26:19.734
THAT SHANK WASN'T REPORTING
THE ADDITIONAL FUNDS.

26:23.708 --> 26:27.451
SO, RYAN SHANK WAS SKIMMING
THE EXTRA FEDERAL MONEY.

26:27.670 --> 26:30.878
13 KIDS -- $700 A MONTH,
12 MONTHS A YEAR.

26:31.090 --> 26:33.581
WE'RE TALKING
AN EXTRA 100 GRAND A YEAR.

26:33.801 --> 26:35.883
YOU WERE TALKING ABOUT ANGER
ON THE RES

26:36.095 --> 26:37.426
CONCERNING FAMILY SERVICES.

26:37.638 --> 26:39.890
MAYBE THE KILLING
WAS PAYBACK.

26:40.099 --> 26:41.930
HECTOR'S
A HIGH-SCHOOL DROPOUT.

26:42.143 --> 26:44.054
HE GETS PAID 200 BUCKS
PER TOOTH.

26:44.270 --> 26:45.680
HOW DOES
HE FIGURE THIS OUT?

26:45.897 --> 26:48.183
RU BY: WALT!

26:48.399 --> 26:50.811
WHAT WAS THE NAME OF THAT
SOCIAL WORKER YOU TALKED TO?

26:51.027 --> 26:53.814
CRYSTAL SHOEMAKER.

26:54.030 --> 26:56.237
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER]

26:56.449 --> 26:58.235
CRYSTAL: I DIDN'T EVEN SEE
THE OTHER CAR.

26:58.451 --> 27:00.817
IT RAN ME
RIGHT OFF THE ROAD.

27:01.037 --> 27:03.824
I SAW THIS MAN APPROACHING,
AND I THOUGHT THAT HE --

27:04.040 --> 27:05.746
HE WANTED TO HELP.

27:05.958 --> 27:07.118
BUT HE GRABBED ME

27:07.335 --> 27:10.327
AND HE TOLD ME TO LEAVE
CHEYENNE CHILDREN ALONE.

27:10.546 --> 27:12.753
THE NEXT ONE I TOOK, HE SAID,
HE'D KILL ME.

27:12.965 --> 27:14.956
CRYSTAL...

27:15.176 --> 27:17.337
WE JUST FOUND
RYAN SHANK'S BODY.

27:17.553 --> 27:19.965
WHAT?

27:20.181 --> 27:21.967
[ SCOFFS ] GOD.

27:22.183 --> 27:25.220
W-WE'RE JUST TRYING TO HELP
THESE POOR KIDS.

27:25.436 --> 27:28.644
THIS MAN WHO TRIED
TO RUN YOU OFF THE ROAD --

27:28.856 --> 27:30.392
WHAT DID HE LOOK LIKE?

27:30.608 --> 27:33.600
HE WAS BIG...

27:33.820 --> 27:35.356
DARK-SKINNED.

27:35.571 --> 27:37.357
CHEYENNE, I THINK.

27:37.573 --> 27:41.407
AND HE HAD A BIG SCAR
UNDER HIS EYE.

27:44.914 --> 27:46.825
NOBODY ON THE RES
WILL TELL MY DEPUTIES
ANYTHING ABOUT HECTOR,

27:46.999 --> 27:48.785
SO I NEED YOU
TO TELL ME, HENRY.

27:49.001 --> 27:50.787
WHERE IS HE?
I DO NOT KNOW.

27:51.003 --> 27:53.415
YOU TRYING TO PROTECT HIM?
OR YOU GONNA HELP ME
FIND THESE BOYS?

27:53.631 --> 27:54.871
HOPEFULLY, BOTH.

27:55.091 --> 27:56.877
THREE CHILDREN ARE MISSING.
A MAN IS DEAD.

27:57.093 --> 27:58.879
NOW THAT SOCIAL WORKER
YOU YELLED AT

27:59.095 --> 28:00.710
A COUPLE WEEKS AGO --
SHE WAS RUN OFF THE ROAD

28:00.930 --> 28:02.340
BY A BIG CHEYENNE MAN
WITH,

28:02.557 --> 28:05.720
AND I OUOTE,
"A BIG SCAR UNDER HIS EYE."

28:05.935 --> 28:08.017
WHAT'S IT GONNA TAKE TO CONVINCE
YOU THIS IS NO SPIRIT, HENRY?

28:08.229 --> 28:09.560
I DO NOT KNOW, WALT.
PROOF?

28:09.772 --> 28:11.433
I AM TELLING YOU
NONE OF THIS SOUNDS LIKE HECTOR.

28:11.649 --> 28:13.059
HE IS NOT A KILLER.

28:13.276 --> 28:14.561
I STILL GOT FIVE YEARS
OF HECTOR'S ARREST WARRANTS

28:14.777 --> 28:15.983
BACK AT THE STATION.

28:16.195 --> 28:18.106
THOSE WARRANTS GET FORWARDED
TO U.S. MARSHALS

28:18.322 --> 28:19.607
UNLESS HECTOR
TURNS HIMSELF IN.

28:19.824 --> 28:22.486
IF HECTOR GOES
INTO THE FEDERAL SYSTEM,

28:22.702 --> 28:24.192
HE IS NEVER COMING OUT.

28:24.412 --> 28:26.824
LET HIM COME IN AND CLEAR
HIS NAME IF HE'S INNOCENT.

28:29.167 --> 28:31.374
[ HINGES CREAK]

28:40.469 --> 28:42.334
[CAN RATTLES]

29:08.831 --> 29:10.287
[ GRUNTING ]

29:25.181 --> 29:28.139
[ BREATHING HEAVILY]

29:31.646 --> 29:32.931
[GRUNTS]

29:33.147 --> 29:34.478
HECTOR:
YOU DEAD, LAWMAN?

29:38.778 --> 29:40.643
I DON'T THINK SO.

29:40.863 --> 29:44.526
NEITHER WAS THE FAT MAN
AT THE FOSTER HOME.

29:45.660 --> 29:49.278
WHEN HE WOKE UP,
I WARNED HIM...

29:49.497 --> 29:51.658
TO STOP STEALING
OUR CHILDREN.

29:57.171 --> 29:58.877
I DID NOT KILL ANYONE.

29:59.090 --> 30:02.332
WHERE ARE THE BOYS,
HECTOR?

30:02.551 --> 30:04.963
I HAD A VISION...

30:05.179 --> 30:08.091
OF CHEYENNE CHILDREN RETURNED
TO THEIR RIGHTFUL HOME.

30:08.307 --> 30:11.299
WHAT ABOUT
THE SOCIAL WORKER?

30:11.519 --> 30:16.309
STOP LOOKING FOR THE INNOCENT,
LAWMAN, AND FIND THE BAD.

30:18.234 --> 30:20.520
YOU KNOW, HECTOR,

30:20.736 --> 30:23.113
I CAN'T JUST LET YOU
WALK OUT THAT DOOR.

30:25.866 --> 30:28.027
THIS IS YOU STOPPING ME?

30:29.412 --> 30:31.198
THAT'S WHAT THIS IS.

30:42.383 --> 30:46.467
[ SNORING ]

30:55.646 --> 30:58.183
CADY: DAD...

30:58.399 --> 30:59.809
LOOK I...

31:00.026 --> 31:01.687
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED
TO YOU?

31:01.902 --> 31:04.234
I WON. I THINK.

31:04.447 --> 31:07.359
DID THAT MAN
DO THIS TO YOU?

31:07.575 --> 31:09.031
HECTOR. YEP.

31:09.243 --> 31:10.449
THAT'S HECTOR?

31:10.661 --> 31:13.494
IS -- IS -- IS HE
THIS DOG SOLDIER GUY?

31:13.706 --> 31:16.163
HECTOR'S, UH, TALLER.

31:16.375 --> 31:17.751
DID HE HAVE THE BOYS?

31:17.960 --> 31:19.700
NO.

31:19.920 --> 31:21.706
WELL...

31:21.922 --> 31:24.538
I WORKED ALL NIGHT, LOOKING AT
THE MISSING KIDS' FILES.

31:24.759 --> 31:26.374
AND EACH CASE WAS INITIATED
BY A CALL --

31:26.594 --> 31:29.006
SOMEONE REPORTING NEGLECT
OR ABUSE.

31:29.221 --> 31:30.677
BUT, DAD,
THE WEIRD THING IS THAT

31:30.890 --> 31:33.427
WHEN I TRIED TO CONTACT
ALL OF THESE CONCERNED CALLERS,

31:33.642 --> 31:35.473
THEY ALL TURNED OUT TO BE
THE SAME MAN.

31:35.686 --> 31:37.301
AND HE LIVES ON THE RES.

31:37.521 --> 31:40.137
REALLY?
YEAH.

31:40.358 --> 31:41.848
WHAT DID HE HAVE TO SAY?

31:42.068 --> 31:43.228
WELL, NOTHING NOW,

31:43.444 --> 31:46.060
BECAUSE HE'S IN THE HOSPITAL,
UNCONSCIOUS.

31:46.280 --> 31:47.520
HE WAS ADMITTED
TWO DAYS AGO.

31:47.740 --> 31:49.947
AND HIS WIFE SAYS THAT
HE TOOK A -- A BAD FALL,

31:50.159 --> 31:52.901
BUT THE DOCTORS ARE PRETTY SURE
THAT HE WAS BEATEN.

31:53.120 --> 31:56.112
[ KNOCK ON DOOR]
UM, HENRY ON LINE ONE.

31:59.460 --> 32:03.749
[SIGHS]

32:03.964 --> 32:05.750
FOUND HECTOR.

32:05.966 --> 32:07.172
HENRY: GOOD.

32:07.385 --> 32:09.000
BUT I HAVE SOMETHING BETTER.

32:09.220 --> 32:12.883
COME ALONE.
I JUST CLOSED FOR THE DAY.

32:15.142 --> 32:18.009
HENRY: THEY WERE HERE
WHEN I ARRIVED THIS MORNING,

32:19.605 --> 32:21.220
BACK DOOR WAS WIDE OPEN.

32:21.440 --> 32:23.522
WHO BROUGHT THEM IN?

32:23.734 --> 32:26.316
ASK THEM.

32:30.991 --> 32:33.858
BOYS, YOU DOING OKAY?

32:35.704 --> 32:39.697
PEOPLE ARE GONNA BE
VERY HAPPY TO SEE YOU.

32:39.917 --> 32:41.908
UM...

32:42.128 --> 32:45.086
CAN YOU TELL ME WHO TOOK YOU?

32:47.800 --> 32:49.916
THE DOG SOLDIER.

32:50.136 --> 32:52.923
LET ME GUESS.

32:53.139 --> 32:55.755
TOOK YOU AT MIDNIGHT,
AS THE MYTH GOES.

32:55.975 --> 32:59.684
NO, IT WAS AFTER BED CHECK,
WHICH IS AT 10:00 P.M.

33:06.735 --> 33:08.441
ARE YOU CALLING
FAMILY SERVICES,

33:08.654 --> 33:10.645
OR CAN THEY GO BACK
TO THEIR REAL FAMILIES?

33:10.865 --> 33:15.074
BY LAW...
I SHOULD CALL FAMILY SERVICES.

33:15.286 --> 33:16.696
BUT?

33:16.912 --> 33:21.326
JUST 'CAUSE IT'S LAWFUL
DOESN'T MAKE IT RIGHT.

33:21.542 --> 33:23.624
THIS WE KNOW.

33:28.132 --> 33:30.623
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

33:30.843 --> 33:32.834
HECTOR USED
HIS ONE PHONE CALL.

33:33.053 --> 33:34.042
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA GUESS
TO WHO.

33:34.263 --> 33:36.003
MORNING, SHERIFF.
HELLO, JACOB.

33:36.223 --> 33:38.305
THIS MAN IS BEING HELD WITHOUT
BEING CHARGED WITH A CRIME.

33:38.517 --> 33:40.257
OBJECTION.
LOOK AT HIS FACE.

33:40.478 --> 33:42.719
HECTOR HAS BEEN IN CUSTODY
FOR EIGHT HOURS.

33:42.938 --> 33:44.519
YOU HAVE TO CHARGE HIM
OR LET HIM GO.

33:44.732 --> 33:47.519
ACTUALLY, JACOB, I HAVE 24 HOURS
BEFORE I HAVE TO CHARGE HIM.

33:47.735 --> 33:49.316
ASK YOUR LAWYER.

33:49.528 --> 33:51.029
JACOB: WELL, IF YOU'RE HOLDING
HECTOR FOR KIDNAPPING,

33:51.238 --> 33:52.398
YOU HAVE NO EVIDENCE
TO CHARGE HIM WITH.

33:52.615 --> 33:54.822
REALLY?

33:55.034 --> 33:56.194
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

33:56.410 --> 33:58.401
BECAUSE
IF YOU HAD ANY EVIDENCE,

33:58.621 --> 34:00.236
YOU WOULD HAVE CHARGED HIM
ALREADY.

34:00.456 --> 34:02.697
AND IF THOSE CHILDREN TURN UP
HEALTHY AND UNHARMED,

34:02.917 --> 34:05.033
NOT ONLY WOULD YOU BE FORCED
TO RELEASE HECTOR,

34:05.252 --> 34:07.459
BUT YOU COULD BE SUBJECT
TO A CIVIL SUIT.

34:07.671 --> 34:08.831
YOU YOURSELF COULD BE CHARGED.
YOU COULD BE CH--

34:09.048 --> 34:10.584
YOU AREN'T EVEN LISTENING
TO ME, ARE YOU?

34:10.799 --> 34:13.632
WHAT? NO.
NOT REALLY.

34:13.844 --> 34:15.584
BUT YOU'VE CONVINCED ME.
VIC, RELEASE THE PRISONER.

34:15.804 --> 34:16.839
EXCUSE ME?

34:17.056 --> 34:18.842
WALT,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

34:19.058 --> 34:22.300
I HAD A VISION --
A VISION OF EMPTY POCKETS.

34:22.520 --> 34:24.385
HECTOR'S A HIRED GUN.
HE ONLY WORKS FOR PAY.

34:24.605 --> 34:26.015
THESE BOYS' FAMILIES --

34:26.232 --> 34:27.847
THEY COULD NEVER AFFORD
TO PAY HECTOR, COULD THEY?

34:28.067 --> 34:30.183
THAT IS A GOOD POINT.

34:30.402 --> 34:32.188
SOMEONE ELSE
MUST HAVE PAID HIM --

34:32.404 --> 34:33.689
SOMEONE WITH A LOT OF MONEY.

34:33.906 --> 34:35.442
INTERESTING.

34:35.658 --> 34:38.821
JUST A SHAME THAT VISIONS
NEVER HOLD UP IN YOUR COURTS.

34:39.036 --> 34:41.618
HECTOR...

34:41.830 --> 34:42.956
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

34:44.375 --> 34:46.661
THIS IS ME
LETTING YOU GO.

34:46.877 --> 34:48.663
VIC: I'M SORRY,
BUT I'M CONCERNED.

34:48.879 --> 34:50.494
DID YOU GET A CONCUSSION
LAST NIGHT?

34:50.714 --> 34:52.124
NO, I'M FINE.

34:52.341 --> 34:54.457
THEN WHY ELSE WOULD YOU LET
OUR PRIME SUSPECT GO?

34:54.677 --> 34:56.213
THE BOYS WERE RETURNED
TO THE RED PONY

34:56.428 --> 34:57.588
WHILE HECTOR WAS
IN CUSTODY.

34:57.805 --> 34:58.920
BY WHO?

34:59.139 --> 35:00.800
THEY ALL CLAIM
THE DOG SOLDIER TOOK THEM

35:01.016 --> 35:02.131
AND BROUGHT THEM BACK.

35:02.351 --> 35:03.557
OKAY,
WHAT ABOUT MURDER?

35:03.769 --> 35:05.134
AND ATTEMPTED MURDER?

35:05.354 --> 35:07.595
NOT TO MENTION THE BEATING
THAT HECTOR GAVE YOU.

35:07.815 --> 35:11.057
WALT: SOMETIMES THE BEST WAY
TO CATCH THE KILLER

35:11.277 --> 35:14.519
IS TO MAKE THEM THINK
THEY'RE FREE.

35:21.370 --> 35:24.862
I KNOW WHO'S RESPONSIBLE
FOR THE MURDER OF RYAN SHANK

35:25.082 --> 35:27.073
AND THE THREAT ON YOUR LIFE,

35:27.293 --> 35:29.284
BUT I CAN'T PROSECUTE
WITHOUT YOUR HELP.

35:29.503 --> 35:32.119
SO...
[ SIGHS ]

35:32.339 --> 35:34.045
IS THIS THE MAN
WHO THREATENED YOU?

35:34.258 --> 35:36.874
YES.
HIS NAME'S HECTOR.

35:37.094 --> 35:39.585
HE'S A CHEYENNE MERCENARY.
PRETTY SCARY GUY.

35:39.805 --> 35:40.965
[SIGHS]

35:41.181 --> 35:43.467
HE, UH,
DID THIS TO ME.

35:43.684 --> 35:44.890
[ GASPS ]

35:45.102 --> 35:46.262
DON'T WORRY.

35:46.478 --> 35:47.979
I BROUGHT HIM INTO CUSTODY
LATE LAST NIGHT.

35:48.188 --> 35:49.803
OH.
THAT'S GOOD TO HEAR.

35:50.024 --> 35:52.606
RELEASED HIM
A FEW HOURS AGO.
WHAT?

35:52.818 --> 35:55.230
HE --
HE TRIED TO KILL ME.

35:55.446 --> 35:57.357
AND YOU SAID
HE KILLED RYAN.

35:57.573 --> 35:58.733
I THOUGHT SO.

36:00.576 --> 36:03.192
HE ASSAULTED RYAN,
TOOK THE BOYS AROUND 10:00 P.M.,

36:03.412 --> 36:05.619
RIGHT AFTER
THEIR LAST BED CHECK.

36:05.831 --> 36:07.571
HERE'S WHAT'S CONFUSING.

36:09.043 --> 36:14.754
RYAN MADE A PHONE CALL,
10:34, ALIVE AND WELL.

36:14.965 --> 36:16.501
CALLED YOU.

36:16.717 --> 36:18.628
I TOLD YOU
WE TALKED THAT NIGHT.

36:18.844 --> 36:22.177
RYAN HAD JUST BEEN ASSAULTED.
THE BOYS HAD BEEN KIDNAPPED.

36:22.389 --> 36:24.345
WHY CALL YOU?
WHY NOT MY DEPUTY?

36:24.558 --> 36:26.844
[ CHUCKLES ]
I DON'T KNOW.

36:27.061 --> 36:29.973
HE CALLED TO TELL YOU SOMEONE
HAD DISCOVERED YOUR SCAM.

36:30.189 --> 36:33.602
YOU TAKE CHEYENNE KIDS FROM
THEIR FAMILIES AND PLACE THEM

36:33.817 --> 36:35.682
IN SHANK'S GROUP HOME
AND COLLECT THE FEDERAL MONEY.

36:35.903 --> 36:37.359
[ SCOFFS ]

36:37.571 --> 36:39.778
I DON'T GET ANY EXTRA PAY
FOR RESERVATION CHILDREN.

36:39.990 --> 36:41.400
NOT UP FRONT.

36:41.617 --> 36:44.279
SHANK TOOK THE EXTRA FEDERAL
MONEY AND SPLIT IT WITH YOU.

36:44.495 --> 36:47.282
ALL THOSE CHILDREN
ARE IN BETTER HANDS NOW.

36:47.498 --> 36:50.661
I WAS FOLLOWING UP ON REPORTS
OF ABUSE OR NEGLECT.

36:50.876 --> 36:53.663
ALL THOSE REPORTS
OF NEGLECT OR ABUSE

36:53.879 --> 36:55.415
WERE MADE BY ONE MAN.

36:56.840 --> 36:59.126
HE WAS YOUR PLANT.

36:59.343 --> 37:01.004
HE'D CALL IN
SOME FAKE COMPLAINTS FOR YOU

37:01.220 --> 37:02.585
IN EXCHANGE
FOR A LITTLE MONEY.

37:03.722 --> 37:06.384
YOU STOLE ALL THESE CHILDREN
FROM THEIR HOMES.

37:06.600 --> 37:08.465
I DO
WHATEVER I HAVE TO DO

37:11.230 --> 37:13.937
I'M BETTING YOU DO
WHATEVER YOU HAVE TO DO
TO PROTECT YOURSELF.

37:16.193 --> 37:19.685
I THINK YOU SAW RYAN SHANK
AFTER HE CALLED YOU.

37:19.905 --> 37:22.521
I BET HE WAS SCARED
AFTER SEEING HECTOR.

37:22.741 --> 37:24.606
I BET
HE WANTED TO COME CLEAN,

37:24.827 --> 37:27.819
BUT YOU WEREN'T READY
TO TURN YOURSELF IN, SO...

37:28.038 --> 37:31.451
YOU RAN HIM OVER
REPEATEDLY.

37:31.667 --> 37:35.285
THE NEXT NIGHT,
YOU DROVE YOURSELF INTO A TREE

37:35.504 --> 37:38.712
TO COVER UP THE DAMAGE
TO YOUR CAR.

37:38.924 --> 37:40.539
SHANK HAD DESCRIBED

37:40.759 --> 37:43.751
THE BIG, SCARY INDIAN
WITH THE SCAR TO YOU, SO...

37:43.971 --> 37:46.303
YOU KNEW EXACTLY WHAT TO TELL ME
TO FRAME HECTOR.

37:46.515 --> 37:49.632
I'VE DEVOTED MY ENTIRE LIFE
TO HELPING CHILDREN.

37:51.186 --> 37:53.393
THAT'S CERTAINLY WHAT
A WYOMING JURY WILL SEE.

37:53.605 --> 37:56.972
THEY'LL SEE AN ARTICULATE,
COMPASSIONATE,

37:57.192 --> 38:01.811
WHITE SOCIAL WORKER ACCUSED
WITH CIRCUMSTANTIAL EVIDENCE.

38:02.030 --> 38:03.361
YOU'RE RIGHT.

38:03.574 --> 38:07.442
THEY WON'T SEE THE CYNICAL,
BURNED-OUT SOCIOPATH

38:07.661 --> 38:09.743
JUST OUT FOR HERSELF.

38:09.955 --> 38:13.823
YOU'LL WALK FREE.
LEGALLY, IT'S THE PERFECT CRIME.

38:14.042 --> 38:17.409
BUT THERE'S SOMETHING
YOU'RE FORGETTING.

38:17.629 --> 38:20.416
HECTOR.

38:20.632 --> 38:24.250
HE KNOWS ABOUT YOUR SCAM,
CRYSTAL.

38:24.470 --> 38:26.927
HE ALSO KNOWS YOU TRIED
TO FRAME HIM FOR MURDER.

38:27.139 --> 38:31.758
[ SCOFFS ] RIGHT.
HE'LL MAKE A GREAT WITNESS.

38:31.977 --> 38:35.310
THE SCAR-FACED INDIAN
WHO KIDNAPPED THOSE BOYS.

38:35.522 --> 38:36.898
THE BOYS SAID
IT WASN'T HIM.

38:38.901 --> 38:40.516
THEY SAY
A DOG SOLDIER ABDUCTED THEM.

38:40.736 --> 38:45.526
THE CHEYENNE BELIEVE IN
AN AVENGING WARRIOR SPIRIT.

38:45.741 --> 38:48.949
CAN TAKE ON ANY FORM --
ANIMAL, HUMAN.

38:49.161 --> 38:50.697
AND YOU BELIEVE THAT?

38:50.913 --> 38:52.995
I BELIEVE
IN TRANSFORMATION.

38:55.542 --> 38:58.409
I BELIEVE
WE BECOME VESSELS...

38:58.629 --> 39:02.963
FOR FORCES WE CANNOT CONTROL
OR UNDERSTAND.

39:03.175 --> 39:07.464
WHEN YOU DROVE OVER
RYAN SHANK,

39:07.679 --> 39:12.890
MAYBE IT WAS THE SPIRIT OF
THE DOG SOLDIER WHO GUIDED YOU.

39:13.101 --> 39:18.391
PERHAPS THAT SPIRIT GUIDED ME
ONCE UPON A TIME, AS WELL.

39:21.193 --> 39:23.684
SO...

39:23.904 --> 39:25.440
CONGRATULATIONS.

39:25.656 --> 39:32.073
WITHOUT YOUR CONFESSION,
WE HAVE NO CASE AGAINST YOU.

39:32.287 --> 39:35.654
BUT THE DOG SOLDIER KNOWS
WHAT YOU'VE DONE, CRYSTAL.

39:35.874 --> 39:39.617
AND WHEN HE COMES
FOR YOU...

39:39.837 --> 39:44.922
I'M JUST A PHONE CALL
AND A 20-MINUTE DRIVE AWAY.

39:59.273 --> 40:03.232
I'LL COME
AS FAST AS I CAN.

40:39.479 --> 40:41.640
[GUN COCKS]
